Notes: Startup listed is for the final, guaranteed laser. Shoots a laser for each bit deployed. Startup for these lasers are 5+9, 5+15, 5+21, 5+27. Lasers that go through bits can hit twice: once when traveling to bit, and again after being reflected

Startup listed is for the final, guaranteed laser. Shoots 2 lasers for each bit deployed: one that travels to bit and is reflected, one that shoots directly at opponent. Startup for these lasers are 5+9, 5+15, 5+21, 5+27. Lasers that go through bits can hit twice: once when traveling to bit, and again after being reflected. Damage while traveling to bits is 640
